history.content:
Do you love CS160? You can help lead the next cohort of students as we evolve CS160 into a new studio type course to be taught in the shiny new Jacobs Institute for Design Innovation Building. In Fall 2015 CS160 will undergo a series of transitions. More info can be found here:

http://teaching.paulos.net/cs160_FL2015/

The class will be expanding to 200 students and we are actively recruiting additional teaching staff now (GSIs and Readers). Please apply using the department link below if you are qualified, creative, and adventurous.

https://willow.coe.berkeley.edu/PHP/gsiapp/menu.php (Due May 1st)
